value: Invoke global convenience functions on the empty menubar area.
Tap, hold and scroll to invoke the ⌘-tab app switcher or swipe left/right to directly activate the previous/next app.
Double tap to unsnap all windows on the current screen. Use the secondary modifier for all screens.
Swipe down to minimize all windows. Once for the current screen, twice or with the secondary modifier for all.
Swipe up to unminimize all windows. Once for the current screen, twice or with the secondary modifier for all.
Swipe up, down, left or right to move all snapped windows to the next screen in that direction.
Invoke this gesture on the Spaces preview in Mission Control.
